126 CARTAE RECENTIORES

19 Preeeptum sasine ab Alexandro Archiepiseopo Atheniensi ad episcopatum Sodo- rensem postulato in favorem Patricij Murray filii Anthonij Murray de Doleray super duodecim mercatis terrarum de Newraw quatuor mereatis terrarum ecclesiasticarum

de Madertie cum prato vocato Kirkmedow et terris de Wynmynhill datum 8 Maroij 1561.

20 Resignation be Margaret Hay in Madertie of ane croft of land liand in the said toune of Madertie callit the Welcroft wedset be hir and vmquhile Patrik Baxter alias Smyth hir spous to Williame J ohnestoun in Pertht vpoun the sowme of tuenty merkis in favouris of dene Paule Cunynghame channone of Incheehaffray and also of the rest of nynetene zeiris takkis of ane aiker of land in Wyndmylne [hill] liand in ye said toun yat ar to rin furtbt set be dene Patrik Murray in N ewraw to hir and hir said vmquhile spons. Dated 9 April 1563.

21 Grant by Alexander bisehope of Galloway commendatar of the abbay of Incheffray and convent-thairof in favour of Alexander Murray sone and apperand air to Patrik - Murray of Newrow for all the dayis of his lyftyme of ane yeirlie pensioun of the sowme of twenty tua pundis money of this realme to be liftit of the malis and teynd sylver of N ewraw Burneheid and Burnefute Ward Todhill and Hay grene Thorniehill alias Wallaceland and Wod and Wodland of Ineheeheviot and the Blair adjacent therto. Subscrivit and gevin under the chaptoure seill of the abbay at Inehecheffray
